# SKF (UK) Limited

> UK subsidiary of the global SKF Group, manufacturing precision sliding contact bearings and rod ends for aerospace and defence applications.

## What they do

SKF (UK) designs and manufactures self-lubricating spherical plain bearings, rod ends and journal bearings to customer-specific standards. The company has led the development of sliding contact bearings in the aerospace and defence sector for over 40 years, supported by in-house CNC machining and a range of specialist liner technologies and bearing materials.

## Products and solutions

- **Self-lubricating spherical plain bearings** - customer-specific designs for aerospace and defence applications.
- **Rod ends and journal bearings** - available in aluminium alloys, titanium alloys, steel alloys and beryllium.

## Frameworks, accreditations and memberships

- **Accreditations:** AS/EN/JISQ 9100, ISO 9001, ISO 14001, NADCAP, EASA 145
- **Memberships:** ADS Group

